comment: Mudiay (DEN) does not have part of his hand under the ball when he brings it to a pause and continues his dribble.
Mudiay (DEN) trips, but not as a result of any contact by Delaney (ATL) that affects his SQBR.
Harris (DEN) makes body contact with Schroder (ATL) that affects his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Barton (DEN) moves his pivot foot.
Arthur (DEN) makes contact with Schroder's (ATL) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Sefolosha (ATL) engage on the rebound. The contact is incidental and does not affect either player's ability to retrieve the rebound.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Harris (DEN) makes contact with the ball without affecting Schroder's (ATL) driving shot attempt.
Mudiay (DEN) lands with the ball out of bounds.
Millsap (ATL) makes marginal contact with Mudiay (DEN) on the screen.
Millsap (ATL) makes marginal contact with Arthur (DEN) on his move toward the basket.
Arthur (DEN) makes contact with Millsap's (ATL) arm and body and affects his jump shot attempt.
Millsap (ATL) maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Chandler (DEN).
